Instructions for building an MSG file.

Design and layout art for HTML using the template in this folder, using HTML and Litmus code for HTML Email compatibility.

Then...

Upload or copy to pc. 

Get on a PC. Open the page in a browser (Chrome works well).

Select All, Copy 

Create new blank Outlook email.

Insert a table (3 column, centered)

Paste into center column.

Check alignments and copy.

Save as MSG (Outlook Message Format)

Attache and send.


